% Exercise 1.4. Europeans use A4 paper. Find out its dimensions, and
% show how to draw a square one centimeter on a side with center in
% the middle of an A4 page. (Incidentally, what is the special
% mathematical property of A4 paper?)

% (Incidentally, what is the special mathematical property of A4
% paper?) - aspect ratio is 1:sqrt(2)

% Dimensions: 210x297mm or 21cm x 29.7

% center of page 10.5 cm x 14.85 cm
% 10 14.35

<< /PageSize [595 842] >> setpagedevice

% scale to cm
72 dup scale
1 2.54 div dup scale

% set line width
0.01 setlinewidth

% move origin to center of page
10.5 14.85 translate

% draw square
newpath
-.5 -.5 moveto
1 0 rlineto
0 1 rlineto
-1 0 rlineto
closepath
fill

% checking out rotation
45 rotate

newpath
-.5 -.5 moveto
1 0 rlineto
0 1 rlineto
-1 0 rlineto
closepath
fill

